{"id": "ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1766, "displayName": {"text": "Luv2eat Thai Bistro", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Classic Thai eatery for familiar favorites in a modern dining room, plus outdoor seating.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT200MlNIa3lhMVZyZUVrMU5GbEpjWGxPVDI1MVJuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Ordered the hat yai fried chicken, the curry khao soi, and Thai ice tea.\nThai tea was amazing. Would get it again in a heartbeat. The fried chicken was okay. I liked how juicy and crunchy it was but it didn’t blow me away flavor wise. The sticky rice that came with it was amazing though.\nThe khao soi was good but wish it was a little creamier.\nGood experience overall.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Ordered the hat yai fried chicken, the curry khao soi, and Thai ice tea.\nThai tea was amazing. Would get it again in a heartbeat. The fried chicken was okay. I liked how juicy and crunchy it was but it didn’t blow me away flavor wise. The sticky rice that came with it was amazing though.\nThe khao soi was good but wish it was a little creamier.\nGood experience overall.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Edgar Saliana", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103912010454190073875/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOERKRJHvUcWsXlQo-F3vFyh_SjwT3yhOxWVib9jKdlQut-g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-09T14:26:11.531403172Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT200MlNIa3lhMVZyZUVrMU5GbEpjWGxPVDI1MVJuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT200MlNIa3lhMVZyZUVrMU5GbEpjWGxPVDI1MVJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf253fb9c789:0xaddcf43c6879c47e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGdFpIWktWM1ZNUVhwbWMyeGlORWMyUm5kVFdVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Luv2Eat Thai Bistro was SO good it genuinely made me feel like I got teleported to Thailand. Portions were super generous too. The papaya salad had that perfect punchy flavor, the moo ping skewers were so rich and satisfying I felt full after one already, and the tom yum soup was amazing.\n\nThe curry crab dish — I think it was their crab curry scramble? — was also insanely good and definitely worth ordering. Honestly my stomach wasn’t big enough because there were still so many things on the menu I wanted to try. Already planning round two next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Luv2Eat Thai Bistro was SO good it genuinely made me feel like I got teleported to Thailand. Portions were super generous too. The papaya salad had that perfect punchy flavor, the moo ping skewers were so rich and satisfying I felt full after one already, and the tom yum soup was amazing.\n\nThe curry crab dish — I think it was their crab curry scramble? — was also insanely good and definitely worth ordering. Honestly my stomach wasn’t big enough because there were still so many things on the menu I wanted to try. Already planning round two next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ines", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113711471716904207793/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-th18p-RcksIl_RUVet8DGMudTsFnvM5Wqg8PfID_57xtDA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-23T01:38:44.938534230Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGdFpIWktWM1ZNUVhwbWMyeGlORWMyUm5kVFdVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGdFpIWktWM1ZNUVhwbWMyeGlORWMyUm5kVFdVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf253fb9c789:0xaddcf43c6879c47e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KVk1EZHhkMnBLYWxGSE16azFVbVZDTkVoUFdtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love dives. This one was absolutely exceptional.\n\nThe crab fried rice was divine. The drunken shrimp noodles were sweet and flavorful.\n\nThe chicken larb was the only slightly disappointing dish because it was only good, not exceptional.\n\nI wish I lived here because I still need to try a curry and basically every dish.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love dives. This one was absolutely exceptional.\n\nThe crab fried rice was divine. The drunken shrimp noodles were sweet and flavorful.\n\nThe chicken larb was the only slightly disappointing dish because it was only good, not exceptional.\n\nI wish I lived here because I still need to try a curry and basically every dish.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Shim G", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106199335835831145627/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqvh4fQ6exfURnk4yyL7SGQbBxFa2b_VNqWr9pO7_kOEU3fMTf7g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-16T23:21:51.597627045Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KVk1EZHhkMnBLYWxGSE16azFVbVZDTkVoUFdtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KVk1EZHhkMnBLYWxGSE16azFVbVZDTkVoUFdtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf253fb9c789:0xaddcf43c6879c47e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210U1JYcFBia05hTXpKMGVERnlZMEZpYmtNMlpYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Great Thai food! My favorite was the crab fried rice and the mango sticky rice. I was really excited for the fried chicken sticky rice dish, it was good but I’ve definitely had better. I’d come back here if I was nearby!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great Thai food! My favorite was the crab fried rice and the mango sticky rice. I was really excited for the fried chicken sticky rice dish, it was good but I’ve definitely had better. I’d come back here if I was nearby!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sky B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118152239561180870685/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAtxLCIn45d1A6tgdVc7E6zsQbaHstexS-mMI6Y7Q03QdG-N0v=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-15T01:59:47.366211613Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210U1JYcFBia05hTXpKMGVERnlZMEZpYmtNMlpYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210U1JYcFBia05hTXpKMGVERnlZMEZpYmtNMlpYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf253fb9c789:0xaddcf43c6879c47e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkNFMwWnFVekEwZURaVlZXcEhVamd6Tm5kVU0yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This neighborhood has a fantastic Thai restaurant that serves authentic Thai cuisine, especially southern Thai style. The menu offers a wide variety of options, and you can easily communicate your spice preference to the server. If you’re unsure about a dish, don’t hesitate to ask for more information.\n\nThe service here is exceptional, with friendly and helpful staff. If you have to wait for a table, you can leave your name and party number at the counter and hang out around. When a table becomes available, they’ll call your name.\n\nThere’s a free parking lot, but it’s a bit limited. Additionally, the restaurant only has one restroom, so be prepared for that. Despite these minor inconveniences, everything else is great.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This neighborhood has a fantastic Thai restaurant that serves authentic Thai cuisine, especially southern Thai style. The menu offers a wide variety of options, and you can easily communicate your spice preference to the server. If you’re unsure about a dish, don’t hesitate to ask for more information.\n\nThe service here is exceptional, with friendly and helpful staff. If you have to wait for a table, you can leave your name and party number at the counter and hang out around. When a table becomes available, they’ll call your name.\n\nThere’s a free parking lot, but it’s a bit limited. Additionally, the restaurant only has one restroom, so be prepared for that. Despite these minor inconveniences, everything else is great.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Footprints", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113980568617596058366/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaDNrY4GoqweWdHD47zr1G-nzdrZFFQFS0LydoSTNcyb8mQg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-26T02:08:08.987204166Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkNFMwWnFVekEwZURaVlZXcEhVamd6Tm5kVU0yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkNFMwWnFVekEwZURaVlZXcEhVamd6Tm5kVU0yYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf253fb9c789:0xaddcf43c6879c47e"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJice5PyW_woARfsR5aDz03K0/photos/AWCwydiEpeOaCvjrLP2t1kuPV3DyP4U6DsZN4bdoC6fKbxg3cO5YYAi5Idtj2krZPBNKRBHHSc1ie33uZ2hlCOoEHfQUbPmxTekpk38EfLFS5kkNF2at91950ZbM1ofcyE999b6azKuTlgiO8YnThphL8UjH7XYVVq-Cqt98gpDEaAtsrvf2neJ6TjlBFwDzUKgYN4RbueiYQMJWcFGv52GK9zUaLoFWJTC5YZQ5X5JllqWS0XEVemlKzaEjmINyGwI08FlDTjxaD-lmX9irC_CzXBJ13b5UymzlQHBL_4YzOLCbBI_mOQ97O6czfZvu_0FCG3Uz92JU_DkFyOZ59k6v4I60fb3z_ZhHQLj-Yjax-MnM9atfYl4aZXEbDJ2L_o3iSpzQLGVV_JJful380bOraJdVNoxjmOF0ejF3P9K